commitResults.messageBody:
Users can use "save" command to save their current list of tasks. List
will be loaded on the next instance of launching the program, preserving
the data between each session.

List data is kept in data/LeeKuanYew.txt.

commitResults.messageBody:
Mark and unmark command handling had duplicated logic, except the
boolean flag used when calling the constructor to indicate if the
command is marked or unmarked.

To match DRY conventions, this commit extracts the shared logic of
handling the command into a separate method.
